PR description:

Splits core/cognito.py (monolith mixing hot-path JWT verification with cold-path Cognito admin calls) into auth/cognito_token.py (request-critical, cached JWKS + verify) and auth/cognito_admin.py (invite/delete — rare, network-heavy). Extracts auth-related FastAPI dependencies (get_current_user, require_role) from api/deps.py into auth/deps.py. Moves auth route into auth/routes.py. Uses intermediate re-export shims to ensure every commit is green.